description: Experience luxury living in this one-of-a-kind,rarely available B-Unit residence at 50 Liberty Drive.This premier front-facing unit offers unparallele waterfront views of Boston Harbor and the entire Waterfront through expansive floor-to-ceiling windows in every room creating breathtaking ambiance.The open floor plan showcases a stunning large waterfall island with custom high-gloss white lacquer cabinetry,first class appliances,Sub-Zero refrigerator,wine chiller,Miele dishwasher Wolf gas stovetop,wall oven.Spacious living/dining flows seamlessly to a large terrace,providing panoramic views of the ocean&Harborwalk,perfect for relaxation.Primary bedroom features a gorgeous en-suite bathroom,custom walk-in closet.2nd bedroom features en-suite bathroom&custom closet.Bonus versatile den/guest room,2 garage parking spaces&storage.Amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,boardroom,club room with waterfront terrace.Located near Seaports finest restaurants,cafes,shops,Airport

exclusions: Chandelier In Primary Bedroom & Chandelier In Main Foyer.
